quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"Si lesdi dimmbaama dimmbagol ndii."
  99,2,"Leyydi ndi yaltini dimle hendi."
  99,3,"Neɗɗo o wi'a ko heɓi ndi."
  99,4,"ñande heen lesdi ndi habra kabaruuji mayri."
  99,5,"Won'de ko joom ma wahyii ndi."
  99,6,"Ñande heen yimɓe ɓe njalta heɓe carii ngam ɓe holle golle mu'en."
  99,7,"Kala baɗɗo fotde gabbel jarra e moƴƴere o yi'a nde."
  99,8,"kalo baɗɗo fotde gabbel jarra e bonan'nde kadi ma yii."
